        "created_at": "2025-07-25T23:59:44.851Z",
        "cooked": "<p>it is highly unlikely Signal will every develop support for non-smart phones. luckily for you the app is open source, meaning such apps have been developed. check out this list, and use the filter ‚ÄúSignal App support‚Äù:<br>\n<a href=\"https://josebriones.org/dumbphone-finder\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://josebriones.org/dumbphone-finder</a><br>\nor just check these recommendations from Vice:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.vice.com/en/article/best-dumb-phones/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/1/c17513839549269f48d1c32cdd27693e90845248.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"1B1B1B\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.vice.com/en/article/best-dumb-phones/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"11:00PM - 10 April 2025\">VICE ‚Äì 10 Apr 25</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/459;\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/7/67bc65c374a9bf8e8e8063b4227d11b6fff58d6d_2_690x459.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"896D65\" width=\"690\" height=\"459\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.vice.com/en/article/best-dumb-phones/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Best Dumbphones (for Smarter Phone Use)</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Perhaps a little stupidity is in order. Dumbphones, the partially disconnected alternative to smartphones, are pretty clever.</p>\n\n  <p>\n    <span class=\"label1\">Est. reading time: 20 minutes</span>\n  </p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
