        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/{size}/34172_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-07-26T06:17:35.545Z",
        "cooked": "<p>GrapheneOS removes most of the Google stuff, and everything else that can‚Äôt be removed is sandboxed. So much of Google‚Äôs tracking and ad software is removed that battery life is exponentially improved. I‚Äôve seen people on Reddit claim two or three days before needing a charge.</p>\n<p>Couple Graphene with simply disabling various Google account settings for tracking etc, and remove anything else with adb, and you‚Äôve effectively got a superior device to both feature phones and Googled Android.</p>",
